Privacy Policy for Water Tracker 2023

At Water Tracker 2023, we take your privacy and security seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our app.

What information do we collect?
We collect information that you provide to us when you use our app, such as your water intake data and achievements. We may also collect technical information about your device and how you use our app, such as your IP address, device type, and app usage.

How do we use your information?
We use your information to provide and improve our app, including personalized daily targets and achievements. We may also use your information to communicate with you about our app and related products and services.

How do we protect your information?
We use industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. Therefore, while we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

Do we share your information?
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties unless we provide you with advance notice. This does not include trusted third parties who assist us in operating our app, conducting our business, or servicing you. We may also release your information when we believe it is appropriate to comply with the law, enforce our site policies, or protect ours or others' rights, property, or safety.

Changes to our Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. By continuing to use our app, you acknowledge and agree to the updated Privacy Policy.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at isurulakmal200013@gmail.com.
